00:20:50.318 --> 00:20:52.518
他干这行比我们久多了
He's been doing this a while longer than we have.

370
00:20:52.688 --> 00:20:55.238
我看你真是觊觎那大副的位置了
I guess you really are sucking up for that XO badge.

371
00:20:55.628 --> 00:20:57.148
我已经干脆地拒绝了
Turned him down flat.

372
00:20:57.148 --> 00:20:58.208
不是吧
You kidding me?

373
00:20:59.198 --> 00:21:01.128
当了大副离船长就一步之遥了
You'd be on the short path to Captain.

374
00:21:01.278 --> 00:21:02.358
问题就在这儿
Exactly.

375
00:21:03.408 --> 00:21:07.518
再说  如果接受  我们就不能在一起了
Besides. if I took it. we'd have to stop seeing each other.

376
00:21:08.498 --> 00:21:10.118
这个
Well. You know.

377
00:21:10.448 --> 00:21:12.658
祸福相依嘛
There's that saying about all good things.

378
00:21:17.178 --> 00:21:18.198
我跟你说过的
I told you.

379
00:21:18.198 --> 00:21:20.208
再几次我可能就会离开了
A couple more rotations and I'd be moving on.

380
00:21:21.208 --> 00:21:23.448
再几次的意思
A couple is...

381
00:21:23.448 --> 00:21:25.568
是至少两次以上
you know. two at least.

382
00:21:25.598 --> 00:21:26.688
我以为
I assumed.

383
00:21:28.718 --> 00:21:30.528
过了今天才是明天
There's right now and there's later.

384
00:21:31.008 --> 00:21:32.748
何必为未来发愁呢
Why worry about later. right?

385
00:21:32.748 --> 00:21:33.728
说的对
Right.

386
00:21:35.518 --> 00:21:36.578
来吧  吉姆
Come on. Jim.

387
00:21:36.578 --> 00:21:37.568
来躺下
Lie down.

388
00:21:38.928 --> 00:21:42.548
我保证不碰你
I promise I won't lay a finger on you.

389
00:21:53.938 --> 00:21:54.868
我睡不着
I can't sleep.

390
00:21:54.868 --> 00:21:55.898
我来盯着吧
I'll take over.

391
00:21:57.298 --> 00:21:59.198
到了谷神星请你喝酒
I'll buy you a bottle on Ceres.

392
00:21:59.438 --> 00:22:01.028
来杯好咖啡就行了
I'll settle for a good cup of coffee.

393
00:22:43.038 --> 00:22:47.708
已删除日志

394
00:22:44.248 --> 00:22:45.908
恢复删除日志

395
00:22:46.118 --> 00:22:47.708
信号分析中

396
00:23:10.968 --> 00:23:12.028
救救我
Please help me.

397
00:23:10.688 --> 00:23:12.858
未知求救

398
00:23:13.668 --> 00:23:15.278
有人吗  拜托
Is anybody there? Please.

399
00:23:29.368 --> 00:23:30.548
请救救我
Please help me.

400
00:23:40.798 --> 00:23:43.508
地月
联合国

401
00:23:58.298 --> 00:24:00.008
我跟你说了多少次了
How many times have I told you?

402
00:24:00.008 --> 00:24:01.998
你再这样我要挠你的
This calls for tickling!

403
00:24:02.238 --> 00:24:03.178
不要
No!

404
00:24:04.028 --> 00:24:07.168
不要不要
No. please. no!

405
00:24:08.738 --> 00:24:10.378
你再挠他要尿裤子了
He'll wet himself if you're not careful.

406
00:24:10.378 --> 00:24:13.118
这就是当爷爷奶奶的好处了
That's the advantage of being a grandparent.

407
00:24:13.518 --> 00:24:15.798
有事可以推给他妈妈
I get to hand him off to his mother.

408
00:24:24.088 --> 00:24:26.948
姥姥  你必须得走吗
Amma. Do you have to go?

409
00:24:27.208 --> 00:24:29.078
是的  对不起
Yes. I do. I'm sorry.

410
00:24:29.378 --> 00:24:31.198
我必须和一个人谈谈
There's someone I need to talk to.

411
00:24:31.208 --> 00:24:32.808
人们又要打仗了吗
Are people fighting again?

412
00:24:33.488 --> 00:24:34.418
还没有
Not yet.

413
00:24:35.898 --> 00:24:39.078
所以才需要谈  说出真相
That's why we need to talk. and tell the truth.

414
00:24:42.108 --> 00:24:44.218
当人们不坦诚相待时
When people don't tell the truth.

415
00:24:44.558 --> 00:24:46.348
就会有不好的事发生
it always ends badly.

416
00:24:57.868 --> 00:25:01.838
联合国  黑牢
汉普顿斯岛/纽约

417
00:25:03.438 --> 00:25:05.818
经查你与外行星联盟的某激进组织有关
You've been linked to a radical faction of the OPA.

418
00:25:06.338 --> 00:25:07.528
你只是个送信的吗
Were you just a courier?

419
00:25:10.738 --> 00:25:12.758
他从水舱出来多久了
How long has he been out of the tank?

420
00:25:11.178 --> 00:25:13.768
克里斯金·阿瓦萨罗拉
联合国副秘书长

421
00:25:12.758 --> 00:25:13.738
十小时
Ten hours.

422
00:25:20.528 --> 00:25:23.788
很抱歉真正行星的重力如此痛苦
I'm sorry the gravity of a real planet hurts.

423
00:25:23.998 --> 00:25:25.528
但也正合适
But it's appropriate.

424
00:25:26.158 --> 00:25:27.778
你想伤害地球
You wish to hurt Earth.

425
00:25:28.518 --> 00:25:32.638
而地球正在摧毁你那虚弱的小行星肺
The Earth that is now crushing your weak Belter lungs.

426
00:25:32.638 --> 00:25:35.408
和脆弱的小行星骨头
and your fragile Belter bones.

427
00:25:36.568 --> 00:25:39.728
只要招供  就能结束这种痛苦
All you have to do to make it stop is talk.

428
00:25:41.328 --> 00:25:43.278
你是外行星联盟恐怖分子
You're an OPA terrorist.

429
00:25:43.358 --> 00:25:46.298
你携带了非法隐形技术
You were carrying contraband stealth technology.

430
00:25:46.858 --> 00:25:48.188
用来干什么
What was it for?

431
00:25:52.028 --> 00:25:56.138
一句话就行  我看你也没力气大声说了
A whisper will do. if that's all you can manage.

432
00:26:04.108 --> 00:26:05.878
再十小时
Give him another 10 hours.

433
00:26:07.658 --> 00:26:09.428
还活着的话  打给我
If he survives. call me.

434
00:26:20.648 --> 00:26:21.968
现已到达
Now arriving.

435
00:26:21.968 --> 00:26:23.508
麦迪纳交易区
Medina Exchange District.

436
00:26:46.368 --> 00:26:47.198
怎么了  宝贝儿
What's up. doll?

437
00:26:47.218 --> 00:26:48.848
空气过滤器故障
Cheap-ass air filters crapped out.

438
00:26:48.848 --> 00:26:50.558
这个月第二次了
Second time this month.

439
00:26:52.828 --> 00:26:55.518
我猜这位没少花钱上下打点吧
I guess this guy pays well to be taken care of. huh?

440
00:26:56.668 --> 00:26:59.388
是啊  也没少给我们老板钱  伙计
Yeah. he pays our bosses pretty well. too. pal.

441
00:26:59.748 --> 00:27:02.448
别想着第一天就拯救整个空间站
Look. don't try to save the whole station on your first day.

442
00:27:03.178 --> 00:27:04.128
慢慢来
Pace yourself.

443
00:27:07.898 --> 00:27:08.818
还没下雨吗
Any rain yet?

444
00:27:12.418 --> 00:27:14.898
我们本该没收到的那条求救信号
That distress call we never received.

445
00:27:15.438 --> 00:27:17.118
被标记为了高清信号
it was logged with HQ.

446
00:27:17.708 --> 00:27:20.948
飞船上某个匿名的狗屁好心人干的
By some anonymous. piece-of-shit do-gooder aboard this ship.

447
00:27:20.948 --> 00:27:22.278
至少有人还有灵魂良心
Well. at least somebody has a soul.

448
00:27:22.278 --> 00:27:23.908
我发誓  让我找到那叛徒
I swear. I find the rat...

449
00:27:23.908 --> 00:27:25.738
别看我了  拜尔斯  小心我戳瞎你
Quit lookin' at me. Byers. or I'll put your lights out.

450
00:27:25.738 --> 00:27:26.978
试试看啊  妹子
Any ol' time. girl.

451
00:27:26.978 --> 00:27:30.538
现在我们只能改道了  不然就真是违法了
Now. we're forced to divert. or the firm's legally on the hook.

452
00:27:30.898 --> 00:27:35.188
霍顿  你来指挥这次救援或者说打捞行动
Holden. You'll head up this rescue. or salvage.

453
00:27:35.338 --> 00:27:36.708
管它怎么叫呢
whatever we're calling it.

454
00:27:37.388 --> 00:27:39.098
组建一支穿梭艇小队
Put a shuttle team together.

455
00:27:42.648 --> 00:27:43.898
有什么问题吗  大副
Is there a problem. XO?

456
00:27:44.118 --> 00:27:46.688
是代理大副  长官
Acting XO. sir.

457
00:27:51.968 --> 00:27:52.868
我不去
I ain't goin'.

458
00:27:52.868 --> 00:27:53.868
说什么都不去
No way. no how.

459
00:27:53.868 --> 00:27:55.228
也没想邀请你
Well. you ain't invited.

460
00:27:55.838 --> 00:27:58.008
亚历克斯  通知发信源我们在去的路上了
Alex. ping the beacon that we're on our way

461
00:27:58.008 --> 00:27:59.908
并告诉谷神星那面我们要晚几天了
and let Ceres know that we're gonna be late.

462
00:28:00.018 --> 00:28:00.838
尼嘉德小姐
Ms. Nygaard?

463
00:28:01.358 --> 00:28:02.908
如果我们立刻转向并全速前进
If we flip right now and burn like hell.

464
00:28:02.908 --> 00:28:04.938
我能让船到达五万公里以内的位置
I can get us within 50.000 clicks.

465
00:28:04.988 --> 00:28:05.608
好极了
Oh. great.

466
00:28:05.608 --> 00:28:07.258
接着我们就都会吐自己一身
Then we'll all be puking in our crash-couches

467
00:28:07.258 --> 00:28:09.338
同时货物四散  砸坏飞船
while the cargo busts loose and scuttles the ship.

468
00:28:09.338 --> 00:28:11.108
确保冰都固定好了
Make sure that ice stays put.

469
00:28:11.518 --> 00:28:14.298
奈奥米  骑士号状态如何
Naomi. How's the Knight looking?

470
00:28:14.298 --> 00:28:16.188
就是艘破烂的救生舰
She's one leaky lifeboat.

471
00:28:16.678 --> 00:28:19.518
不过五万公里的真空应该撑得住
She should be able to manage 50.000 clicks of vacuum.

472
00:28:19.528 --> 00:28:20.938
好  那你也一起
All right. then you're on board.

473
00:28:26.528 --> 00:28:27.478
这里霍顿
This is Holden.

474
00:28:28.088 --> 00:28:32.938
我们收到CA-2216862附近的求救信号
We've logged a distress call near CA-2216862.

475
00:28:33.078 --> 00:28:35.608
我们有义务改变航向进行响应
We're obliged to change our course and respond.

476
00:28:35.668 --> 00:28:38.208
确保你们的加速剂分配器充足
Make sure your acceleration drug dispensers are full.

477
00:28:38.208 --> 00:28:39.998
此次将是高重力加速度操作
This will be a High-G maneuver.

478
00:28:39.998 --> 00:28:41.528
准备转向加速
Prepare for flip and burn.

479
00:28:57.738 --> 00:28:59.248
饮料来了
Here comes the juice.

480
00:30:32.298 --> 00:30:33.178
我不明白
I can't figure out

481
00:30:33.178 --> 00:30:35.978
为什么舰长会让你负责这次的小行动
why Cap would put you in charge of this little excursion.

482
00:30:36.168 --> 00:30:39.338
他依然觉得他在培养我干大事
Well. he still thinks he's grooming me for bigger things.

483
00:30:39.348 --> 00:30:40.998
那他就是在浪费时间
Then he's wasting his time.

484
00:30:41.668 --> 00:30:42.958
我一直这么跟他说的
That's what I keep telling him.

485
00:30:47.638 --> 00:30:49.778
如果是你女朋友登记了那条求救信号
If your girlfriend logged that distress call.

486
00:30:50.908 --> 00:30:53.158
她很长一段时间都好过不了了
she's gonna be living it down for a long time.

487
00:31:00.188 --> 00:31:00.988
是我干的
I did it.

488
00:31:07.448 --> 00:31:08.838
我就是没办法就这么算了
I just couldn't shake it.

489
00:31:11.798 --> 00:31:13.928
我是你的话就不会说出来
I'd keep that to myself if I were you.

490
00:31:20.478 --> 00:31:22.028
有什么好消息  伙计们
What's the good word. y'all?

491
00:31:23.838 --> 00:31:24.698
好吧
All right.

492
00:31:25.398 --> 00:31:27.828
我亲爱的老破船今天怎么样
How's my sweet old rust bucket today?

493
00:31:28.348 --> 00:31:30.648
我猜一会就知道了  不是吗
Well. I guess we'll find out. won't we?

494
00:31:30.918 --> 00:31:31.768
是吧
I guess so.

495
00:31:34.438 --> 00:31:35.148
好了
Okay.

496
00:31:39.858 --> 00:31:41.468
事先声明  伙计们
So just for the record. guys.

497
00:31:41.728 --> 00:31:43.388
我可不想待在这儿
I don't wanna be here right now.

498
00:31:43.388 --> 00:31:44.468
我也不想
Me neither.

499
00:31:44.648 --> 00:31:46.108
但我们都在这了
But here we are.

500
00:31:46.598 --> 00:31:48.148
一个开心的小队
One big. happy unit.

501
00:31:48.518 --> 00:31:50.318
骑士号  你们的飞行计划已经设定
Knight. your flight plan is set.

502
00:31:50.438 --> 00:31:53.008
两小时后到达目的地  喷气式飞行
It'll be a two-hour trip to the Tango. flying tea-kettle.

503
00:31:53.008 --> 00:31:54.358
谢谢  坎特伯雷号
Thank you. Canterbury.

504
00:31:54.808 --> 00:31:55.738
不客气  骑士号
Welcome. Knight.

505
00:31:56.428 --> 00:31:57.488
一路平安
Godspeed.

506
00:31:57.488 --> 00:31:58.628
发现有任何不对劲
If you see anything that seems off.

507
00:31:58.628 --> 00:32:00.528
马上收拾东西回来
you pack up the toys and come on home.

508
00:32:00.698 --> 00:32:02.098
绝不逞能  舰长
No heroes. Captain.

509
00:32:02.578 --> 00:32:03.908
准备离开船舱
Clear to leave the barn.

510
00:32:04.118 --> 00:32:05.008
好运
Good luck.

511
00:32:34.508 --> 00:32:35.198
真的吗
Really?

512
00:32:38.928 --> 00:32:40.148
她下班了
She's off the clock.

513
00:32:41.148 --> 00:32:42.858
她可以自己跟我说
Then she can tell me that.

514
00:32:55.518 --> 00:32:56.888
要我就盯紧点那家伙
I'd keep an eye on that guy.

515
00:32:57.038 --> 00:33:00.698
我听说他空闲时收集月岩
I hear he collects moon rocks in his spare time.

516
00:33:01.958 --> 00:33:03.448
想知道他还喜欢什么吗
You wanna know what else he's into?

517
00:33:04.158 --> 00:33:07.068
我只是来找你的
Now. I'm just lookin' out for you.

518
00:33:08.898 --> 00:33:10.548
我需要女人的直觉
I need a woman's intuition.

519
00:33:12.508 --> 00:33:13.298
她是谁
Who is she?

520
00:33:13.298 --> 00:33:15.898
她只是一起失踪案的主角
Oh. she's just a missing persons case

521
00:33:16.438 --> 00:33:18.698
案子我不能说  你懂的
I'm not "permitted to discuss." you know.

522
00:33:20.368 --> 00:33:22.268
朱莉叶·安德洛墨达·毛
Juliette Andromeda Mao.

523
00:33:23.018 --> 00:33:25.368
她是太阳系最富有的单身女子
She's the richest bachelorette in the system.

524
00:33:26.608 --> 00:33:28.338
谷神星上的富家女孩
Now what would a rich girl do

525
00:33:29.448 --> 00:33:32.468
想彻底激怒父亲的话会怎么做呢
to really piss daddy off on Ceres?

526
00:33:32.468 --> 00:33:33.858
你是问我怎么做的吗
Are you asking what I did?

527
00:33:35.618 --> 00:33:37.708
跟每一个能找到的汉子乱搞
Bang every space bucker I could find.

528
00:33:39.028 --> 00:33:40.268
这可没什么帮助
That's not helpful.

529
00:33:40.658 --> 00:33:41.388
抱歉  米勒
Oh. I'm sorry. Miller.

530
00:33:41.388 --> 00:33:42.978
你是来找我帮忙的吗
Did you come here for my help?

531
00:33:43.488 --> 00:33:44.398
拜托
Come on.

532
00:33:45.868 --> 00:33:47.858
承认吧  你想我
Admit it. You miss me.

533
00:33:48.188 --> 00:33:49.858
想念这样的聊天
You miss these little chats.

534
00:33:50.518 --> 00:33:52.158
晚安  米勒
Good night. Miller.

535
00:33:59.928 --> 00:34:01.398
吃点东西吧  老天
Eat something. for God's sake.

536
00:34:01.398 --> 00:34:02.568
你看上去糟透了
You look like hell.

537
00:34:15.598 --> 00:34:18.978
海岩号运输舰
CA-2216862行星轨道

538
00:34:22.238 --> 00:34:24.588
配置与注册信息一致
Config matches the registry information.

539
00:34:26.068 --> 00:34:27.708
绝对是海岩号
It's definitely the Scopuli.

540
00:34:28.258 --> 00:34:31.528
除了求救信号外没有红外线或电磁波信号
No IR or Electro-mag other than the distress beacon.

541
00:34:27.818 --> 00:34:31.948
求救信号
来源  未知
距离

542
00:34:32.038 --> 00:34:33.348
看上去反应堆已关闭
Looks like the reactor's shut down.

543
00:34:33.348 --> 00:34:35.198
但没有发生辐射漏泄
but no radiation leakage.

544
00:34:36.828 --> 00:34:40.148
边上像个大洞的是什么
What about that thing that looks like a big hole in the side?

545
00:34:41.898 --> 00:34:44.388
激光雷达显示那就是个大洞
Uh. LADAR says it's a big hole in the side.

546
00:34:46.998 --> 00:34:49.618
坎特号上的雷达在一百万公里范围内
Well. the big array on the Cant's reading no one

547
00:34:49.618 --> 00:34:51.308
没发现任何人
within a million clicks.

548
00:34:51.308 --> 00:34:53.138
看来只有我们在这里
Looks like we're the only game in town.

549
00:34:53.138 --> 00:34:55.498
我们来了  看见了  离开了
Well. we came. we looked. we. uh. left.

550
00:34:56.488 --> 00:34:58.458
没人会知道我们上没上那艘船
No one's gonna know if we set foot on that thing.

551
00:35:02.288 --> 00:35:03.208
带我们过去
Take us in.

552
00:35:03.918 --> 00:35:04.828
亚历克斯
And. Alex.

553
00:35:05.058 --> 00:35:07.068
要是那船上藏着什么麻烦
If something nasty's hiding in that ship.

554
00:35:07.068 --> 00:35:09.598
我们马上撤退  把身后的东西都烧成灰
we bolt like hell and melt anything behind us into slag.

555
